https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRs79c3r.jpg&h=646ad439&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9dkbros.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9dkbros.jpg&h=9cb5d5b8&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7h6BCu8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7h6BCu8.jpg&h=23f412a4&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f474a0db53034ea2e279dd0775cb6c88ab0f8246","tid":1663120,"uid":42734,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T08:21:53.000Z","msg":"有樣野好重要<br />\n好多和理非可能覺得自己出來行行企企幫唔到d咩所以匿係屋企<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n唔好諗你出黎做到d咩<br />\n你不如諗下如果你唔出來，得返前線幾十人會變成點"},{"pid":"75c24289e5bc3f806153dd6d8b4f130ee1279be9","tid":1663120,"uid":312698,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T08:22:38.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"29d38cfab8d7275c380a1fc8930938664c6c2114","tid":1663120,"uid":42734,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T08:24:23.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"073d3cd58e34515003d8c9e5d92b2ac35c189b1e","tid":1663120,"uid":268123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T08:27:17.000Z","msg":"【香城施政報告2019】群策群力 轉危為機<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1656908\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1656908</a><br />\n<br />\n<em><strong>政治問題</strong></em><br />\n<br />\n- 重塑公民身分戶口政策保障國家、香港安全和利益<br />\n- 取消18區區議會、建立地域市政議會<br />\n- 禁止公務人員在任前、任內和任後獲港外榮典<br />\n- 改善高鐵一地兩檢操作方式<br />\n<br />\n<em><strong>便民基建</strong></em><br />\n<br />\n- 興建東鐵、西鐵快速線並完善輕鐵和西鐵聯乘關係<br />\n- 完善機場集體運輸並加強機場、港珠澳大橋協同發展<br />\n- 修正港鐵、巴士可加可減機制<br />\n<br />\n<em><strong>醫療、教育方向</strong></em><br />\n<br />\n- 興建至少四所新區域全科醫院<br />\n- 以減少送院為目標的社區護理服務<br />\n- 重塑教育, 著重知識、技能層次分工<br />\n<br />\n求正評及幫推！"},{"pid":"d78e46a73d21376011f3c251557844fd26dfbb34","tid":1663120,"uid":42734,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T08:55:43.000Z","msg":"仲有一樣<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">唔好再叫班人形垃圾做popo！！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n佢地唔係好可愛既卡通人物，係強姦犯、殺人犯呀！"},{"pid":"86d9ef53044ecdda834ab0ed90c781c65e918477","tid":1663120,"uid":36065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T08:56:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}